title: All for One
overview: Trainees are in different classes, with the help of senior mentors, they will receive strict training. Through sweat and hard work, they will become a class of strong, talented and professional trainees. 10 teams will be made and the contestants will compete as teams, through evaluations, few teams will be eliminated each round. Two groups will debut in the end, one will be the winning team while the other team is the top 9 contestants based on voting (excluding those who are in the winning team).
